data.description: Nestled on 10 tranquil acres with only two large acreage properties as your bordering neighbors. Enjoy a morning cup of coffee watching the sunrise over Brasada Ranch from the back covered deck or the incredible Cascade Mountain sunsets off the front porch. The functional floor plan has the primary bedroom/ensuite on the main level with double vanities, solid counter tops, soaking tub, double shower heads and two walk in closets along with a large den off the vaulted entryway.  10' ceilings throughout most of the home. Kitchen has granite slab counter tops, soft close drawers and cabinets, wine fridge and SS appliances. Gather with friends in the Great Room area or in the upstairs bonus room.  Upstairs is a wonderful separate space for your family and friends with 3 large bedrooms and full bath.  Outside 10x16 Storage shed, Chicken coop, raised garden beds and low maintenance native landscape.  Shared well with one 10 acre parcel yet to be built. Shared entry gate/gravel driveway
